    "In this case, the tractable observeddata likelihood and smoothing process can be efficiently calculated (conditional on parameters) using a Kalman filter (Kalman, 1960) and joint state and parameter inference can proceed in the Bayesian context via Markov chain Monte Carlo (e.g.",
